1.Switch Statements
    switch (switch-expression)
    {
        case value1: statement(s)1;
                        break;

        case value2: statement(s)2;
                        break;

        ...
        case valueN: statement(s)N;
                     break;
        default: statements(s)-for-default;
    }

2. While Loops
    while (loop-continuation-condition)
    {
        //loop body
        stements
    }
3. Do - While loop
    do
    {
        //loop body;
        statement(s);
    } while (loop-continuation-condition)

4. For loop: for loop for adding one, two variavbles and for loops for multiplying one or two variables

